{
  "description": "Demonstrates cellular_automata transform which generates binary modulation patterns from elementary cellular automata (like Wolfram's Rule 30 or Rule 110). The pattern is deterministic but appears chaotic, creating structured randomness.",
  "motifs": {
    "steady_tone": [
      "329.63:0.3",
